example Net::SSLeay:

    Net::SSLeay::version(..)

example (output from openssl):
'session_protocol' retruns string used by openssl (like TLSv1.2)

    Protocol  : TLSv1.2

'fallback_protocol'

    Note: output from openssl:      TLSv1.2
    Note: output from Net::SSLeay:  TLSv1_2


